summary:
This is my first mod, so please be honest with me. I will learn more an more to improve myself.

This mod adds a little Camp near Whiterun. You can find Jule, a Khajit-Vendor there. Furthermore other usefull stuff is located around the two tents.

This mod contains:
- new AI Jule (Khajit)
- 4 chests
- 2 tents
- a forge
- much of Nirnroot
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod, so please be honest with me. I will learn more an more to improve myself.

This mod adds a little Camp near Whiterun. You can find Jule, a Khajit-Vendor there. Furthermore other usefull stuff is located around the two tents.

This mod contains:
- new AI Jule (Khajit)
- 4 chests
- 2 tents
- a forge
- much of Nirnroot
- food in barrels
- weapons
- a vendor (Jule)

... and other stuff. Have fun!! :)
author: bratak1991
